  "body": "\r\n### Description\r\n\r\n[comment]: # (Feature or Bug? i.e Type: Bug)\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\n\r\n[comment]: # (Describe the feature you would like, or briefly summarise the bug and what you did, what you expected to happen, and what actually happens. Sections below)\r\n*Summary*:  I've noticed some improper currency conversions on the \"Wallet\" when switching the \"Main currency\" options from the \"Profile\" menu.\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\n[comment]: # (Describe what you expected to happen.)\r\nAlways to see proper conversions. \r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n[comment]: # (Describe what actually happened.)\r\nThey are wrong for some currencies. \r\n\r\nHere are a few examples considering USD 51.11 as a reference amount I'll be converting from:\r\n\r\n* Switch to BGN - Status displays 141.36 BGN which is incorrect! The correct conversion should equal to ~ 84.49 BGN.\r\n* Switch to AFN - Status displays 132 AFN. The correct value should be ~  71.55 AFN\r\n* Switch to BMD - Status displays 0 BMD. The correct value should be ~ 51 BMD\r\n* Switch to BND - Status displays 31.68 BND. The correct value is ~ 70.28 BND.\r\n\r\nPlease note that I haven't gone through all of the available currency options so the list above is incomplete. Please also note that some of the conversions are fine (like USD to EUR for example). \r\nI've checked all of the mentioned as improper conversions with at least 2 of the top currency conversion calculator results on Google. \r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n[comment]: # (Describe how we can replicate the bug step by step.)\r\n\r\n1. Open Status\r\n2. Log in\r\n3. Make sure that your \"Wallet\" have some assets. Request some if it doesn't.\r\n4. Take a note of the current \"Total value\" of your \"Wallet\". \r\n5. Navigate to \"Profile\" -> \"Main currency\" and select a different one. \r\n6. Go back to the \"Wallet\" menu and check the \"Total value\"\r\n\r\n### Solution\r\n[comment]: # (Please summarise the solution and provide a task list on what needs to be fixed.)\r\n*Summary*: \r\n\r\n- Check/Update the API and the implementation.\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n[comment]: # (Please do your best to fill this out.)\r\n* Status version: \r\n\r\nAndroid - 0.9.19 (6034)\r\niOS - 0.9.19 (6031)\r\n\r\n[comment]: # (Android or iOS.)\r\n* Operating System: Android and iOS\r\n\r\n![usd](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/5781465/41506820-af43a862-722d-11e8-9992-9f7c9fec49a0.png)\r\n\r\n![bgn](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/5781465/41506822-b44d0e70-722d-11e8-996e-fc3ef8da7fab.png)\r\n\r\n",
